            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "        Angular anisotropy is found from the Least-",
                "  Squares fit to measurements at various angles",
                "  according to the formula",
                "           W(PHI)/W(90.deg.)=1+A*COS(PHI)**2,",
                "  where PHI is the angle between the neutron direction",
                "  and the fragment direction"
              ]
